            "content_html": "<h2>求职应该选择大厂还是小厂</h2>\n<h3>起因</h3>\n<p>上上周，有个同学来找我，他说自己在startup干了两年，觉得还是要去大厂，准备写简历和面试。<br>\n我说你现在这家公司不是挺好的么，在云服务的细分领域做</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://valaxy.site/posts/career planning/career essay/Should I choose a large company or a small company\" target=\"_blank\">https://valaxy.site/posts/career planning/career essay/Should I choose a large company or a small company</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://valaxy.site/posts/career planning/career essay/Should I choose a large company or a small company",
            "title": "求职应该选择大公司还是小公司",
            "date_modified": "2025-03-21T00:00:00.000Z",
